
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 06 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lymph nodes, axilla' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Borderline, central fat hilus preserved' radio button is enabled
And 'Pathological' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Borderline, central fat hilus preserved' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Right' checkbox
Then 'Short axis diameter (SAD)' input field is enabled

When I select 'Left' checkbox
Then 'Short axis diameter (SAD)' input field is enabled
